\title{rich text editing in [Bike](jms-0085)}
\author{jonmsterling}
\date{2023-08-29}

\p{[Bike](jms-0085) is a rich text editor, but one that (much like [GNU TeXmacs](van-der-hoeven-2020)) avoids the classic pitfalls of nearly all rich text editors, such as the ubiquitous and dreaded \em{“Is the space italic?!”} user-experience failure; I will not outline [Bike](jms-0085) [innovative approach to rich text editing](https://www.hogbaysoftware.com/posts/bike-rich-text/) here, but I suggest you check it out for yourself.}
